{
  "id": "com.applemusic.source",
  "name": "Apple Music",
  "versionCode": 4,
  "versionName": "0.2.0",
  "author": "Replica0110",
  "description": "Apple Music 搜索源插件",
  "apiVersion": 1,
  "includeDirs": ["lib"],
  "icon": "icon.png",
  "entry": "source.js",
  "capabilities": ["searchSongs", "getLyrics", "searchCovers"],
  "configFields": [
    {
      "key": "lyrics_provider_notice",
      "title": "歌词源说明",
      "group": "歌词",
      "type": "markdown",
      "defaultValue": "### 歌词源说明\n\n- **第三方**：通过 [PaxSenix Apple Music Lyrics](https://lyrics.paxsenix.org/apple-music/lyrics) 获取歌词，不需要 Apple Music 登录态。\n- **官方**：通过 Apple Music 官方接口获取歌词，需要填写网页登录态 Cookie 中的 `media-user-token`。\n\n官方源限制：\n\n- `media-user-token` 所属地区需要与下方选择的地区一致。\n- `media-user-token` 会过期，失效后需要重新获取。\n- 高频请求或批量匹配可能触发 Apple 风控、限流或临时封禁。\n- 只有账号和地区有权限访问的歌曲才可能返回官方歌词。"
    },
    {
      "key": "lyrics_provider",
      "title": "歌词源",
      "group": "歌词",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "third_party",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "third_party",
          "label": "第三方"
        },
        {
          "value": "official",
          "label": "官方"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "media_user_token",
      "title": "Media User Token",
      "group": "歌词",
      "type": "password",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "",
      "dependency": {
        "match": {
          "key": "lyrics_provider",
          "value": "official"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "region",
      "title": "地区",
      "summary": "用于 Apple Music catalog storefront，例如 cn/us/jp。需要和 media-user-token 所属地区匹配",
      "group": "请求",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "cn",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "cn",
          "label": "中国大陆",
          "summary": "cn"
        },
        {
          "value": "us",
          "label": "美国",
          "summary": "us"
        },
        {
          "value": "jp",
          "label": "日本",
          "summary": "jp"
        },
        {
          "value": "kr",
          "label": "韩国",
          "summary": "kr"
        },
        {
          "value": "tr",
          "label": "土耳其",
          "summary": "tr"
        },
        {
          "value": "hk",
          "label": "香港",
          "summary": "hk"
        },
        {
          "value": "tw",
          "label": "台湾",
          "summary": "tw"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "language",
      "title": "语言",
      "summary": "用于 Apple Music localization 参数",
      "group": "请求",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "zh-Hans",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "zh-Hans",
          "label": "简体中文",
          "summary": "zh-Hans"
        },
        {
          "value": "zh-Hant",
          "label": "繁体中文",
          "summary": "zh-Hant"
        },
        {
          "value": "en-US",
          "label": "English",
          "summary": "en-US"
        },
        {
          "value": "ja-JP",
          "label": "日本語",
          "summary": "ja-JP"
        },
        {
          "value": "ko-KR",
          "label": "한국어",
          "summary": "ko-KR"
        },
        {
          "value": "tr-TR",
          "label": "Türkçe",
          "summary": "tr-TR"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "cover_size",
      "title": "封面大小",
      "summary": "Apple Music 封面图片尺寸",
      "group": "封面",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "3000",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "500",
          "label": "500 × 500"
        },
        {
          "value": "1000",
          "label": "1000 × 1000"
        },
        {
          "value": "3000",
          "label": "3000 × 3000"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "minHostApiVersion": 1
}
